#: ../../introducing.rst:1031
msgid ""
"This screen is used to set the size (or upper limit) of the virtual machine."
" If planning to install |trueos| as the guest OS on the virtual machine, "
"**increase the size to at least 20 GB** or an error will display during the "
"|trueos| installation. If planning to install KDE, GNOME, multiple desktop "
"managers, or applications within the virtual machine, choose at least **50 "
"GB**. Whatever size is set, be sure the computer has enough free disk space "
"to accommodate the size chosen. Use the :guilabel:`folder` icon to browse to"
" a directory on disk with sufficient space to hold the virtual machine."
